{
  "3253340": {
    "name": "Push 3D",
    "steam_appid": 3253340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras/d291418f2958d7c0e057b092b0d8c6e6.avif?t=1764831839\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Push 3D is a digital re-creation of the Push board-game, created by Dave Shedden.</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, players take turns moving a game piece around a Hex-based board. On their turn, a player can make two out of three choices. They can flip a tile, making it a &quot;Slip&quot; surface, where moving across them will cause the piece to slip to the other side. Alternatively, players can move their piece in a given direction, or, if they are in a direct line with each other, they can &quot;Push&quot; their opponent backwards.   <br><br><strong>Can you out-think your opponent as the board fills with Slip tiles? Are you cunning enough to be the Player that pushes the other off the board, sealing your victory as champion? Prove it now, by playing a friend in this online multi-player game.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras/a0c5679462d3b0a3971a8b795b942403.avif?t=1764831839\" width=1022 height=365 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-Player practice, or Two-Player local machine &quot;Hotseat&quot; Mode. <strong><i>(Coming Soon)</i></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vs Computer Mode, where you play against an automated opponent. <strong><i>(Coming Soon)</i></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Multiplayer Mode, where you use a matchmaking system to connect online with other players.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras/5958273fa9dda0167ffd16cc3b5a2f34.avif?t=1764831839\" width=1021 height=221 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A monthly Leaderboard, to see how you stack against the World! <strong><i>(Coming Soon)</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras/8c3b518fb6fc4b64480e329d63d76133.avif?t=1764831839\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras_big/8c3b518fb6fc4b64480e329d63d76133.webp?t=1764831839 width=1560 height=853 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Art Deco visual style to set the mood.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A period appropriate soundtrack to match the visual era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras/f0847e530e3d476fb1045ab8a6de9b61.avif?t=1764831839\" width=1018 height=426 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hosts and Local Players can configure the game with a number of settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253340/extras/2711d1703bf63a61cc4d10f2852b67e7.avif?t=1764831839\" width=1018 height=209 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization choices for the Local Player, like piece selection and piece color selection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And finally, Steam Achievements!</p></li></ul>",
